title: asset-conversion-precompiles expose pool management
doc:
- audience: Runtime Dev
  description: Add createPool, addLiquidity, and removeLiquidity functions to the
    asset-conversion precompile, enabling EVM contracts to manage liquidity pools
    directly. Also refactors common helpers (caller lookup, path validation) for reuse
    across swap and liquidity operations.
crates:
- name: pallet-asset-conversion-precompiles
  bump: minor
